    <item>
      <title>Blocked select logging (deadlock finding) in golang</title>
      <link>https://purpleidea.com/blog/2023/05/26/blocked-select-logging-in-golang/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 May 2023 01:21:22 -0400</pubDate>
      <guid>https://purpleidea.com/blog/2023/05/26/blocked-select-logging-in-golang/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve been writing some massively concurrent code for &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/purpleidea/mgmt/&#34;&gt;mgmt&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;lately. The concurrency makes it incredibly bug prone. In this case it&amp;rsquo;s usually&#xA;races or deadlocks. I&amp;rsquo;ve got a new trick to make the process more pleasant.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;text-decoration:underline; font-weight: bold;&#34;&gt;The Problem&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m sure many of you have written some code like this before:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-golang&#34; data-lang=&#34;golang&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#080;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;// just a small excerpt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;select&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;{&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt;someEvent:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#080;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;// some awesome thing happened!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;-&lt;/span&gt;ctx.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#00a000&#34;&gt;Done&lt;/span&gt;():&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#x9;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a2f;font-weight:bold&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;ctx.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#00a000&#34;&gt;Err&lt;/span&gt;()&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;span style=&#34;color:#bbb&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And during debugging, you might have gotten frustrated and added some printf&amp;rsquo;s:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
